node.text:
This cream puff from @baristartcoffee_sg was heavenly! SWIPE LEFT to drool.

It is filled with Hokkaido BIEI Jersey Milk custard cream, and topped off with delectable crisps and sugary bits.

A decadent treat that was luscious but surprisingly not overwhelming.

I bought 3 for $12 from the branch at Tras Street.

Baristart Coffee
Address: 65 Tras Street
Opening Hours: Daily 10am to 10pm
Phone: +65 6904 3168
This is next on my list! 🤤
